http://www.thehindu.com/news/national/andhra-pradesh/Heart-rending-tragedy/article14022565.ece

Three kids were drowned in a tank on the outskirts of Srikakulam on Tuesday when they went for taking a bath there.The deceased have been identified as Lavanya (9), Manikantha (7) and Geeta (6). According to police, they went to take a bath in the tank at Kanuguluvanipeta asTuesday was a holiday on account of the Republic Day.However, what was meant to be an amusement for the children turned tragic when they met with watery grave. The police and revenue officials went to the spot and made arrangements for recovery of the bodies.Srikakulam MLA G. Lakshmidevi went to the spot and inquired about the incident.